    "3 innu 1 PAGE TWO Midway 8340 Entered a secondclass matter June 24 1988 at the post office at Saint Paul Minnesota under the Act of March 3 1879 Mail subscribers should give office two weeks notice of change of address to insure receiving paper without interruption ADVERTISING RATES WILL BE FURNISHED UPON APPLICATION Cecil E Newman R Jones E Bradley Gordon Parks Jimmy Lee The RECORDER believes no man should be denied the right to contribute his best to humanity As long as that right is denied any man no mans rights are inviolate Whenever Joe Louis enters the ring he chalks up another victory for better race relations in the United States The masses of people who never hear of our great scientists artists and other types of out standing people know of the Brown Bomber Unfortunately there are a number of people in this world of ours who cannot appreciate anything but a sock on the jaw a kick in the pants or the business end of a shooting iron The usual picture painted of Negroes makes them appear timid and always in need of the protection of some person from another racial group The evil of"
